            "answer_text": "As a musician, the only thing I always carry with me is a small leather pouch on my keyring with a flap that closes with a popper. Inside is a handmade metal guitar pick. Inscribed on the guitar pick is I love you x and my daughter\u2019s name. She and her mother got it made for me, and gave it to me for my birthday a few years ago. I never actually play with it, partly because the pick is metal and has a rough edge and would basically saw through strings in a few hours, and partly because it\u2019s too personally valuable to me. But I carry it with me everywhere. ",
